\n<br />\n我真係有好努力去學過同適應，希望佢地唔好再俾呢啲說話我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明呀，我真係明<br />\n日日返去好似行刑咁"},{"pid":"97d0ef20363ce98dbfbb8f480aed2f04d942c89c","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T19:57:16.000Z","msg":"再加上我本身有depression加OCD, 所以我可能令大家覺得我依家自尋煩惱....其實最初我set左自己呢份工最起碼要做一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5c7863f5d5df3c3f3a9f1351143e0d8739f281","tid":35003,"uid":36609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T19:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打 fg? 趁後生仲有得簡 覺得唔岩咪搵第份試下 可能更適合自己呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗理人地目光咁多既 巴打加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以想聽日遞信</blockquote><br />\n遞咪遞<br />\n洗咩理咁多"},{"pid":"3c0c912960543423cc3c77d3a15713e93e5747ab","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T19:58:31.000Z","msg":"其實依家做2個幾月就走，心裡已經好自責"},{"pid":"89468764f10ce5412173e935eaa935bcb2d71b38","tid":35003,"uid":10819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T19:59:02.000Z","msg":"mpo?"},{"pid":"6b79f2704714aca07ebb363f65148f8ca8f06f58","tid":35003,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實依家做2個幾月就走，心裡已經好自責</blockquote><br />\n咁既心理質素好難出社會揪"},{"pid":"b45b0a9d4a6d738034137a789926797c6a515850","tid":35003,"uid":54077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:00:53.000Z","msg":"梗係趁後生試下邊樣適合自己<br />\n做人已經好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番工仲要咁大壓力會爆煲"},{"pid":"e257b4a8d3863d20dc96419b4d07cce7c35da372","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:00:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>mpo?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80759e153f6ef65c1f451e54f235bbe1b110e814","tid":35003,"uid":36609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實依家做2個幾月就走，心裡已經好自責</blockquote><br />\n大家明買明賣<br />\n重要大把人走<br />\n自咩責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a0a00ee635a555940186f016e66a9d525d2778","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實依家做2個幾月就走，心裡已經好自責</blockquote><br />\n咁既心理質素好難出社會揪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係我第一份工 只係我第一份想好好試下嘅工"},{"pid":"a7c77075e987d6665c0278241bab747698515829","tid":35003,"uid":11462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:02:36.000Z","msg":"唔啱做咪走 就算做夠一年都唔會啱做"},{"pid":"ee8183a1ce1fc56ed9057b5028e990cd9654c41c","tid":35003,"uid":36609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實依家做2個幾月就走，心裡已經好自責</blockquote><br />\n咁既心理質素好難出社會揪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係我第一份工 只係我第一份想好好試下嘅工</blockquote><br />\n你揾條仔唔岩都分手啦"},{"pid":"e36e367722fa9ab5f26f4a98d4d8ebf811bf3fdb","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實依家做2個幾月就走，心裡已經好自責</blockquote><br />\n大家明買明賣<br />\n重要大把人走<br />\n自咩責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最主要係走左 好似應驗左佢話驕生慣養果啲說話，雖然我已經唔係同期第一批人走<br />\n不過當然聽日會遞信，只係想呢個星期好過少少 呻下"},{"pid":"ddfd95cfa60808f180e74c1afeceb44259c7ae9b","tid":35003,"uid":36609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:04:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實依家做2個幾月就走，心裡已經好自責</blockquote><br />\n大家明買明賣<br />\n重要大把人走<br />\n自咩責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最主要係走左 好似應驗左佢話驕生慣養果啲說話，雖然我已經唔係同期第一批人走<br />\n不過當然聽日會遞信，只係想呢個星期好過少少 呻下</blockquote><br />\nwho care?"},{"pid":"5ee3cfb42e7987355c3639a9b6aa6193cca3660c","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:04:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔啱做咪走 就算做夠一年都唔會啱做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你啱"},{"pid":"8ac49399d5c97bc2a0fbadae578c49d6018f3038","tid":35003,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:05:10.000Z","msg":"辭職都咁緊張，你真係幾唔捱得<br />\n又或者有病"},{"pid":"e784c447ed79b27b0eb7be20ff1cd4c650050594","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:05:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n大家明買明賣<br />\n重要大把人走<br />\n自咩責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最主要係走左 好似應驗左佢話驕生慣養果啲說話，雖然我已經唔係同期第一批人走<br />\n不過當然聽日會遞信，只係想呢個星期好過少少 呻下</blockquote><br />\nwho care?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI care. 雖則我都知無謂"},{"pid":"1c9734ccb1a0302ced7f1a90a3bbaa968fcb0a52","tid":35003,"uid":10819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:06:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>mpo?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早兩年係入邊做過一年<br />\n勸op你早走早著啦"},{"pid":"7fafb6de25b5f79ae77cb35311b3c035bd801195","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:06:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>辭職都咁緊張，你真係幾唔捱得<br />\n又或者有病</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有，我都好努力唔想被影響"},{"pid":"f91e623e1118f0b0f74691fdeea0b7586e65ac27","tid":35003,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:06:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;其實依家做2個幾月就走，心裡已經好自責</blockquote><br />\n咁既心理質素好難出社會揪&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n唔係我第一份工 只係我第一份想好好試下嘅工</blockquote><br />\n想試既工通常鳩<br />\n<br />\n例如設計 廣告<br />\n<br />\n睇上去好似好有創意<br />\n<br />\n做到入去 真係有得畀你做藝術家咩<br />\n<br />\n越係夢想工 越係呃鳩人搵笨<br />\n<br />\n搵食工一定悶架啦"},{"pid":"6d5fc9781ecc37bf37fca2b47dbbf8232e2e86d9","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:08:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>mpo?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早兩年係入邊做過一年<br />\n勸op你早走早著啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打過來人？聽聞做到一年已經可以上神枱"},{"pid":"c6ea2b8b91d4260045021bb443d71d21a04bc3c1","tid":35003,"uid":36609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n大家明買明賣<br />\n重要大把人走<br />\n自咩責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最主要係走左 好似應驗左佢話驕生慣養果啲說話，雖然我已經唔係同期第一批人走<br />\n不過當然聽日會遞信，只係想呢個星期好過少少 呻下</blockquote><br />\nwho care?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI care. 雖則我都知無謂</blockquote><br />\n比－個外人影響自己？<br />\n咁唔通人話你肥就減肥<br />\n話你瘦就增肥咩<br />\n呢個世界冇人可以滿足所有人"},{"pid":"3bb358d51e8829ef0762cb9f49075aea27b581a2","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nwho care?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI care. 雖則我都知無謂</blockquote><br />\n比－個外人影響自己？<br />\n咁唔通人話你肥就減肥<br />\n話你瘦就增肥咩<br />\n呢個世界冇人可以滿足所有人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明白巴打意思 所以我辭職係因為想自己似番個人 做一份起碼開心嘅工作"},{"pid":"aecd618172560cc57eea27554114e33b849b2b8b","tid":35003,"uid":43370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:12:38.000Z","msg":"好高人工？"},{"pid":"fe54f3db9bdb3760203e049b65caf21d735909d9","tid":35003,"uid":36609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nwho care?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI care. 雖則我都知無謂</blockquote><br />\n比－個外人影響自己？<br />\n咁唔通人話你肥就減肥<br />\n話你瘦就增肥咩<br />\n呢個世界冇人可以滿足所有人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明白巴打意思 所以我辭職係因為想自己似番個人 做一份起碼開心嘅工作</blockquote><br />\n快Ｄ訓<br />\n諗下一星期後去邊度"},{"pid":"e6788fd7e2cff2f944331f30edb3f9e8fbafacc2","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:14:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好高人工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFG來講唔錯，但事實好多時攞唔到full salary , 有同事range 大到差4k 都有"},{"pid":"8b56b0ccc2ba5b6ab450cc4f8cdf0d6a020bfb93","tid":35003,"uid":36609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:14:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nwho care?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI care. 雖則我都知無謂</blockquote><br />\n比－個外人影響自己？<br />\n咁唔通人話你肥就減肥<br />\n話你瘦就增肥咩<br />\n呢個世界冇人可以滿足所有人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明白巴打意思 所以我辭職係因為想自己似番個人 做一份起碼開心嘅工作</blockquote><br />\n快Ｄ訓<br />\n諗下一星期後去邊度玩下</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4175df914f82afa5ee8ef66af6e983edb77ee4fd","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n比－個外人影響自己？<br />\n咁唔通人話你肥就減肥<br />\n話你瘦就增肥咩<br />\n呢個世界冇人可以滿足所有人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明白巴打意思 所以我辭職係因為想自己似番個人 做一份起碼開心嘅工作</blockquote><br />\n快Ｄ訓<br />\n諗下一星期後去邊度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好期待下星期 最想好好瞓一覺"},{"pid":"d9fb78975033c97ea39ef875c332c125d3f158a4","tid":35003,"uid":43080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:16:47.000Z","msg":"下次唔開心就早走早著啦<br />\n除非你好等錢洗<br />\n失眠算小事，有fd試過壓力性胃痛食唔到野入廠"},{"pid":"9d4c83a27a8acf8fed27d7221ce1e9fb7d7e410d","tid":35003,"uid":27111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:16:48.000Z","msg":"其實間間公司都標籤90後。<br />\n<br />\n都係因航，依家返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0aa98a8187547ad70fe262e4f1cfbf0ab3dc96","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下次唔開心就早走早著啦<br />\n除非你好等錢洗<br />\n失眠算小事，有fd試過壓力性胃痛食唔到野入廠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n錢係其次 本身唔想個cv 好似好jumpy <br />\n同事們真係大壓力 成日見有同事係個位喊 或者掉野"},{"pid":"57c85f54efc17827903fb22d74b8066f8c362b4f","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實間間公司都標籤90後。<br />\n<br />\n都係因航，依家返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明白有少部分九十後可能真係工作態度唔好，但唔應該對每個九十後都先入為主，明明好多非九十後工作能力態度都更差"},{"pid":"4bf4445602b59eda1f198f76df64273e6dfc6222","tid":35003,"uid":6900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:27:48.000Z","msg":"趁重可以一個星期通知走就好走, 之後跟得多野又要一個月重辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c54d4d396185ab340d9a2c6bb84d20ea658aa86","tid":35003,"uid":43370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好高人工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFG來講唔錯，但事實好多時攞唔到full salary , 有同事range 大到差4k 都有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔岩做咪走<br />\n東家唔打打西家"},{"pid":"1a407a2b55138786192ecbc001df4e94cddf49fa","tid":35003,"uid":9098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實間間公司都標籤90後。<br />\n<br />\n都係因航，依家返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明白有少部分九十後可能真係工作態度唔好，但唔應該對每個九十後都先入為主，明明好多非九十後工作能力態度都更差</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撐樓主；認同你所講既野<br />\n好多上咗位既60/70後甚至上緊位既80後，<br />\n都異化咗去玩辦公室政治同弄權為樂，<br />\n所以有時候唔好將所有責任攬上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw，樓主有Depress底既，<br />\n我建議你衡量下自己對工作內容既適應程度同抗壓程度；<br />\n我唔想Blame每個人既心理質素不如其他人，<br />\n但我認為係一個好機會比樓主你審視自己，<br />\n對下一份工作、同下一份工既你有更好既Planning<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da2a94cf35ca251aed89b59455a3a576aae37bf","tid":35003,"uid":9098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:34:06.000Z","msg":"漏咗句，辭職是要勇氣的；加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d835604ddb69cb9adaf59d109db3f6804d177a7","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實間間公司都標籤90後。<br />\n<br />\n都係因航，依家返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明白有少部分九十後可能真係工作態度唔好，但唔應該對每個九十後都先入為主，明明好多非九十後工作能力態度都更差</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撐樓主；認同你所講既野<br />\n好多上咗位既60/70後甚至上緊位既80後，<br />\n都異化咗去玩辦公室政治同弄權為樂，<br />\n所以有時候唔好將所有責任攬上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw，樓主有Depress底既，<br />\n我建議你衡量下自己對工作內容既適應程度同抗壓程度；<br />\n我唔想Blame每個人既心理質素不如其他人，<br />\n但我認為係一個好機會比樓主你審視自己，<br />\n對下一份工作、同下一份工既你有更好既Planning<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打，其實我都有反省過之後嘅工作，都會傾向想搵番一啲唔駛咁over attentive 嘅工作，捱唔係問題，但唔好每日單單打打又expect 我新丁一啲錯都冇，當然我唔會話犯錯我冇責任，但至少有多少少空間俾我適應同改善"},{"pid":"0e129e52fd98d943aaa3d18f00a6acf3b7b38ede","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:40:46.000Z","msg":"另外都想confirm 下，聽日遞信7日通知，last day 係星期日，但我係番一至五，咁來緊星期六日都仲有人工架Ma? 感謝巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065072c1962611b45a9744dfdf39ed771d60a587","tid":35003,"uid":61022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:42:30.000Z","msg":"走咗就算，咪諗咁多"},{"pid":"076d02ce4e4e17258612c0fbe3596d10b456df89","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:48:57.000Z","msg":"另外都想confirm 下，聽日遞信7日通知，last day 係星期日，但我係番一至五，咁來緊星期六日都仲有人工架Ma? 感謝巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0eeff5c868074ae5f03aeb0f51a8b815bfaa90","tid":35003,"uid":43370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外都想confirm 下，聽日遞信7日通知，last day 係星期日，但我係番一至五，咁來緊星期六日都仲有人工架Ma? 感謝巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要睇佢點計<br />\n有公司日薪計working day<br />\n有公司日薪除30/31日<br />\n除30/31果種就六日都出糧<br />\nWorking day 計法就冇"},{"pid":"70c2127d013fb716b4d119b8ef5e5d506ca26967","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>另外都想confirm 下，聽日遞信7日通知，last day 係星期日，但我係番一至五，咁來緊星期六日都仲有人工架Ma? 感謝巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要睇佢點計<br />\n有公司日薪計working day<br />\n有公司日薪除30/31日<br />\n除30/31果種就六日都出糧<br />\nWorking day 計法就冇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打 我係除30/31日果種"},{"pid":"c3d3ef438dce27c1e430f34fecafb372d095caa1","tid":35003,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T23:09:47.000Z","msg":"過多兩個鐘就要返新工<br />\n但想放飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09cf9280a6a417cdcdc0b9d934c977f69adde5c1","tid":35003,"uid":19925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T23:17:09.000Z","msg":"唔岩做真係好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c699fe64c73ac2cb1cc109c20fd8dc8b4d26a4fe","tid":35003,"uid":63532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T23:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我都明冇辦法控制人地把口，只係覺得個精神壓力好大想呻下，呢份工搞到我發夢都見到office, 放工都唔開心，因為已經好anxious 12個鐘後又要番來.....<br />\n<br />\n我真係有好努力去學過同適應，希望佢地唔好再俾呢啲說話我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第一份工都係咁做酒店，結果一星期就收皮。你唔洗覺得係自己唔捱得嘅九十後，咪當係篩緊有咩工原來係唔啱自己。呢個世界唔一定工揀人，人都可以揀工，唔啱就閃！"},{"pid":"3c6b158853064ecad8688766fa03ffd1d15824b6","tid":35003,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T00:34:11.000Z","msg":"行番公司嘅路行到好頹"},{"pid":"fd89da059ef24ff983c9d69e1da95825a003d4fc","tid":35003,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T00:35:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行番公司嘅路行到好頹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食個靚早餐先返個人會有衝勁啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e0d705159e4f4f9669b81137652a3cc4e5c7f4","tid":35003,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T00:39:19.000Z","msg":"世界好大，你走左後，大把雞會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b9a7b82613b2cabfb49760b41add8519eecf84","tid":35003,"uid":56758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"試用期內好快d走<br />\n過左先走好笨柒<br />\n我就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14b39e3d13d78b8dba99d9b7d61bee633d25042","tid":35003,"uid":33441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:38:42.000Z","msg":"The best is yet to come"},{"pid":"ea1d118ac2439de6f7b50190d5927cc183906dda","tid":35003,"uid":40422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T03:42:51.000Z","msg":"明年今日?"},{"pid":"40704e38c6c0ee7477b018e57cf75c105e63755c","tid":35003,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:06:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實間間公司都標籤90後。<br />\n<br />\n都係因航，依家返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明白有少部分九十後可能真係工作態度唔好，但唔應該對每個九十後都先入為主，明明好多非九十後工作能力態度都更差</blockquote><br />\n人地唔係因為你九十後就歧視你，而係因為你先歧視九十後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b0570b29c92e5b8d435a003e2628ce1a652357","tid":35003,"uid":2506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:09:15.000Z","msg":"份工好高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89771dd04a675c91ccafcf2f87712973e6e979f","tid":35003,"uid":415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"辭職真係唔使諗咁多，啲老屎忽冇人理係要出口術刷下存在感㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 九十後驕生慣養又點？慘得過你有青春佢地冇，淨係可以坐喺位講呢樣講嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFG頭一兩年轉工好正常，唔搵又點知邊份工啱呢？最緊要唔好企喺公司嗰邊諗，因為公司係剝削你嘅源頭，就算你走咗會影響運作，都佢死佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祝你快啲搵到份好工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}